---
import PageLayout from '../../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

export const prerender = true;

const lang = 'en';
const title = 'Mission';
const pageTitle = 'Mission';
---

<PageLayout title={title} lang={lang} pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <p>The mission of the Public Association «Counterpart-Sheriktesh» is to promote the building of a democratic, legal state, develop civil society institutions, protect human and civil rights and freedoms in the Kyrgyz Republic.</p>

  <h2>Our Goals</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Strengthening democratic institutions and civil society</li>
    <li>Protection of human rights and freedoms</li>
    <li>Legal education of the population</li>
    <li>Community development</li>
    <li>Environmental safety and sustainable development</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Key Areas of Work</h2>
  <p>The organization monitors human rights compliance, conducts educational programs, provides legal assistance to the population, and implements projects on civil society development and environmental protection.</p>
</PageLayout>
